                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we'll learn how to organize your presentation.\nA clear structure helps the audience follow your ideas easily.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/94450421-decb-43e5-b67f-b9d45bdf8344-Structured-Presentations---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, tell the audience how many points you will cover.\nUse: \"I'll cover [number] things. [point 1], [point 2], and [point 3].\"\nExample: \"I'll cover three things. The problem, our solution, and the results.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/94450421-decb-43e5-b67f-b9d45bdf8344-Structured-Presentations---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "When you move to a new point, use a transition.\nUse: \"Now let's move to [next point].\"\nExample: \"Now let's move to our go-to-market plan.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/94450421-decb-43e5-b67f-b9d45bdf8344-Structured-Presentations---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "You can also connect two ideas together.\nUse: \"The main point here is [insight]. This links to [next topic].\"\nExample: \"The main point here is that 60% of users drop off at checkout. This links to our redesign plan.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/94450421-decb-43e5-b67f-b9d45bdf8344-Structured-Presentations---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
